### **4. 24_ChartPulsePanel**  
**Description:**  
Live-updating line chart for numeric data using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# ChartPulsePanel - Real-Time Line Chart Viewer

ChartPulsePanel creates smooth real-time visualizations of numeric streams for monitoring or analysis.

## Features
- Dynamic chart display  
- Lightweight and fast  
- Suitable for simulations and sensors  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_ChartPulsePanel.git
cd 24_ChartPulsePanel
python visualize.py
